{"data":{"properties":{"created_at":1629825428000,"events":{},"identifier":"interactables/radio","modified_at":1629825428000,"properties":{"Radio":[{"name":"palette","description":"<p>Alters the displayed color scheme.</p>\n","types":["auto","inverse","inherit","accent","dark","light","alert","affirmative","negative"]},{"name":"size","description":"<p>Renders the <code>Radio</code> at a different sizes.</p>\n","types":["tiny","small","medium","large","huge"]},{"name":"variation","description":"<p>Alters the appearance of the <code>Radio</code>.</p>\n","types":["flush"]},{"name":"active","description":"<p>Renders the <code>Radio</code> with <code>aria-pressed</code> attribute, and styles the <code>Radio</code> as if it where being clicked.</p>\n","types":["boolean"]},{"name":"disabled","description":"<p>Renders the <code>Radio</code> with <code>disabled</code> attribute, and styles the <code>Radio</code> partially transparent.</p>\n","types":["boolean"]},{"name":"name","description":"<p>Sets the form name of the <code>Radio</code>.</p>\n","types":["string"]},{"name":"state","description":"<p>Sets the checked state of the <code>Radio</code>.</p>\n","types":["boolean"]},{"name":"value","description":"<p>Sets the value sent whenever the parent <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> is submitted.</p>\n","types":["string"]}]},"sections":[{"identifier":"radio","level":1,"text":"Radio"},{"identifier":"imports","level":2,"text":"Imports"},{"identifier":"states","level":2,"text":"States"},{"identifier":"palette","level":2,"text":"Palette"},{"identifier":"size","level":2,"text":"Size"},{"identifier":"flush","level":2,"text":"Flush"}],"snippets":[{"identifier":"radio-preview","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Form,\n        Radio,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n\n    let logic_state = \"vanilla\";\n</script>\n\n<Text is=\"strong\">\n    Select an Ice Cream Flavor\n    <Text is=\"sup\">{logic_state}</Text>\n</Text>\n\n<Stack spacing=\"small\" margin_top=\"small\">\n    <Form.Group\n        logic_name=\"radio-preview\"\n        bind:logic_state\n    >\n        <Radio\n            id=\"radio-preview-bubblegum\"\n            palette=\"accent\"\n            size=\"tiny\"\n            value=\"bubblegum\"\n        >\n            Bubblegum\n        </Radio>\n\n        <Radio\n            id=\"radio-preview-chocolate\"\n            palette=\"accent\"\n            size=\"tiny\"\n            value=\"chocolate\"\n        >\n            Chocolate\n        </Radio>\n\n        <Radio\n            id=\"radio-preview-vanilla\"\n            palette=\"accent\"\n            size=\"tiny\"\n            value=\"vanilla\"\n        >\n            Vanilla\n        </Radio>\n    </Form.Group>\n</Stack>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Radio Preview"},{"identifier":"radio-imports","script":"<script>\n    import {Radio} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>","syntax":"html","title":"Radio Imports"},{"identifier":"radio-states","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Radio,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    class=\"radio-states\"\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    spacing=\"medium\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">DEFAULT</Text>\n        <Radio />\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">STATE</Text>\n        <Radio state />\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">ACTIVE NO-STATE</Text>\n        <Radio active />\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">ACTIVE STATE</Text>\n        <Radio active state />\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">DISABLED NO-STATE</Text>\n        <Radio disabled />\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">DISABLED STATE</Text>\n        <Radio disabled state />\n    </div>\n</Stack>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.radio-states strong) {\n        display: block;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Radio States"},{"identifier":"radio-palette","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Form,\n        Radio,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Form.Group logic_name=\"radio-palette\">\n    <Stack\n        class=\"radio-palette\"\n        orientation=\"horizontal\"\n        spacing=\"medium\"\n        variation=\"wrap\"\n    >\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">DEFAULT</Text>\n            <Radio />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">ACCENT</Text>\n            <Radio palette=\"accent\" />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">DARK</Text>\n            <Radio palette=\"dark\" />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">LIGHT</Text>\n            <Radio palette=\"light\" />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">ALERT</Text>\n            <Radio palette=\"alert\" />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">AFFIRMATIVE</Text>\n            <Radio palette=\"affirmative\" />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">NEGATIVE</Text>\n            <Radio palette=\"negative\" />\n        </div>\n    </Stack>\n</Form.Group>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.radio-palette strong) {\n        display: block;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Radio Palette"},{"identifier":"radio-size","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Form,\n        Radio,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Form.Group logic_name=\"radio-size\">\n    <Stack\n        class=\"radio-size\"\n        orientation=\"horizontal\"\n        spacing=\"medium\"\n        variation=\"wrap\"\n    >\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">DEFAULT</Text>\n            <Radio />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">TINY</Text>\n            <Radio size=\"tiny\" />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">SMALL</Text>\n            <Radio size=\"small\" />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">MEDIUM</Text>\n            <Radio size=\"medium\" />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">LARGE</Text>\n            <Radio size=\"large\" />\n        </div>\n\n        <div>\n            <Text is=\"strong\">HUGE</Text>\n            <Radio size=\"huge\" />\n        </div>\n    </Stack>\n</Form.Group>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.radio-size strong) {\n        display: block;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Radio Size"},{"identifier":"radio-flush","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Form,\n        Menu,\n        Radio,\n        Spacer,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Menu.Container>\n    <Menu.Heading>Sort By</Menu.Heading>\n\n    <Form.Group\n        logic_name=\"radio-flush\"\n        logic_state=\"ascending\"\n    >\n        <Menu.Label for=\"radio-flush-ascending\">\n            Ascending\n            <Spacer />\n            <Radio\n                value=\"ascending\"\n                palette=\"accent\"\n                variation=\"flush\"\n            />\n        </Menu.Label>\n\n        <Menu.Label for=\"radio-flush-decending\">\n            Decending\n            <Spacer />\n            <Radio\n                value=\"decending\"\n                palette=\"accent\"\n                variation=\"flush\"\n            />\n        </Menu.Label>\n    </Form.Group>\n</Menu.Container>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Radio Flush"}],"title":"Radio"},"render":"<h1 id=\"radio\">Radio</h1>\n<p><code>Radio</code> is typically used to present a set of mutually-exclusive options to the end-user, which they can then choose from.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/interactables/radio/radio-preview?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/interactables/radio/radio-preview?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"imports\">Imports</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-html snippet-highlight\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Radio<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"states\">States</h2>\n<p>You can control the state of the <code>Radio</code> via the <code>active</code>, <code>disabled</code>, and <code>state</code> properties.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/interactables/radio/radio-states?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/interactables/radio/radio-states?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"palette\">Palette</h2>\n<p>You can change the color palette of the <code>Radio</code> via the <code>palette</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/interactables/radio/radio-palette?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/interactables/radio/radio-palette?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"size\">Size</h2>\n<p>You can change the size of the <code>Radio</code> via the <code>size</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/interactables/radio/radio-size?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/interactables/radio/radio-size?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"flush\">Flush</h2>\n<p>You can change the appearance of the <code>Radio</code> to be flush with the rest of the Application content via the <code>variation</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/interactables/radio/radio-flush?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/interactables/radio/radio-flush?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a>"}}